  <note reference-line="18" id="5">
    <original>sammiñjitaṃ (sī. syā. kaṃ. pī.)</original>
    <type>auto</type>
    <snippet> – ‘‘eso, bhante, āyasmā sāriputto pubbārāme migāramātupāsāde bhikkhūnaṃ ajjhattasaṃyojanañca puggalaṃ deseti bahiddhāsaṃyojanañca. Haṭṭhā, bhante, parisā. Sādhu, bhante, bhagavā yenāyasmā sāriputto tenupasaṅkamatu anukampaṃ upādāyā’’ti. Adhivāsesi bhagavā tuṇhībhāvena. Atha kho bhagavā – seyyathāpi nāma balavā puriso samiñjitaṃ </snippet>
    <match>samiñjitaṃ</match>
    <alternatives>
